title: The KVB  "Sleepwalking" - Converse Red Light Session
description:
www.converse-music.com

Blending reverb-soaked shoegaze with minimalist electronic production, the KVB swept us away with their industrially-tinged take on post-punk pop during their recent Converse Red Light Session.
